# Tests

- Prefer focused unit tests for chunking and timing edge cases.
- Test adapters with original, minimal fixtures.
- Assert HTTP status and stable payload fields, not implementation details.
- Keep one real short MP4 smoke test and avoid long rendering fixtures.
- Cover Unicode, empty input, invalid settings, and temporary-file cleanup.
